             Connect IQ Store's product catalogue lags the SDK — uploading the
             newest hardware generation (CIQ API 6.x plus the 2025 Instinct/Descent
             lines) is rejected with ERROR_WHILE_PROCESSING_MANIFEST because the
             store doesn't have those products registered yet. Those 26 devices are
             deferred; add them back here (and rebuild the .iq) as the store starts
             accepting them. See docs/store-submission.md §1. Drawables resolve by
             screen-family qualifier (resources-<deviceFamily>/). -->
